 ------------------------------------
 XPath2.js - Pure JavaScript implementation of XPath 2.0 parser and evaluator
 ------------------------------------
 Copyright (c) 2012 Sergey Ilinsky
 Dual licensed under the MIT and GPL
 ------------------------------------

 About:
 ===============
   XPath2.js is an open-source JavaScript library that implements XPath 2.0
   It can run against any standard-complient DOM Core Level 3 model,
   yet it can be easily adjusted for other implementations (check DOMAdapter.js)

 Structure:
 ===============
   src/ - Contains implementation of XPath 2.0 parser and evaluator
   dom/ - Contains API objects that mimic DOM Level 3 XPath 1
   test/unit/ - Contains unit.js XPath 2.0 tests

 Usage:
 ===============
   You can link library sources with DOM API to dom/xpath2.js
   XPath2Evaluator, XPath2Exception and XPath2Result objects available
